Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone. I'm Mori\NHayashi, an intern at Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first "Fresh Monday" in 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to call you in with a little\Nmomentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2018, I want to do my best as a\Nteacher who can express everyone's\Nfeelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'd like to take attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, Aso!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been 3 years since I became a\Njunior high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is tough! 2018 Tendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, go ahead, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the second year of middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsugumi Aritomo, second year of\Nmiddle school. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of you will get a new badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be in the middle school for 3\Nyears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for ruining your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Yoshida!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was small, but it's 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And lastly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it won't start from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you just gave your name card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels weird. I feel like I haven't\Nbecome one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a trainee at a real school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a 3rd year junior high school\Nstudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is this some kind of prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The countdown has already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? You're a 2nd year junior high\Nschool student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are 2nd year junior high\Nschool students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really 2nd year junior high\Nschool students?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to hide your age from that\Nage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 2nd year junior high school student,\NAritomo Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tanaka looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your smile is intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I was a little bit older.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you were a transfer student,\Nyou might become a senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've grown a lot in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And today, we have a blackboard behind\Nyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You all drew this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the giraffe cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The giraffe is the biggest problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving up on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I look like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of bad feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew a lot of Manji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of Manji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep up with your uncle, so\Nyou're drawing a lot of Manji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Manji, Manji, Manji, Manji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you fail today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, "Let's grow from here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, "This year has been a tough\Nyear."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a long story, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment I came in, I thought, "This\Nyear is going to be tough."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, Aritomo came to the\Ndressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, "Mr. Mori, there's a dropout\Ntest."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, you brought out a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mori doesn't know much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Aritomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand this question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to get fired this\Nyear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a pinch since Sakura Nagumi\Nstarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I'm sorry for the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a hurry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at the answer and take out\Nmy smartphone, Tanaka is already strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka is so strict that it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be released in the future,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already regretting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the start of my 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I want to have fun with\NFreshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,These members...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Okada's handover party is still\Ngoing on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard he's feeling better now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think you can be at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's start right away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The first hour is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, 2018...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,2018...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead, he's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,2018 Fresh Monday Meas Back Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it, I can't say it. It's\N2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to make it more exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a theme for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to shout it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A word you want to shout for 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, "This is what will happen\Nto me in 2018."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can say, "I want her to fix this\Nthis year."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikurin, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to shout out what you feel\Nthis year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with Yoshida.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cut her lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of Yoshida's baseball bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida's baseball bat is traumatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to say to Yoshida in\N2018?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori sensei, Mori Mori is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine because Momoe is there at the\Ntime of the announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can do it too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a part where you only rely on\NYoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "Yoshida, please!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep putting pressure on him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about this at the press\Nconference yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that if I don't say\Neveryone's name, someone will get mad
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After the graduation ceremony, the\Ngraduates will be like "Why did you say\Nmy name today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eh, is that so?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato will get really mad at you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that happens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, it's me all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, it's Yoshida
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go with Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka is already
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miyasu's first time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka you were noisy today
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so excited
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be a good age
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miku and Miki, the last letters are a\Nbit different
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujihira is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I make mistakes every time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever called Miku\N"Miku"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzu and Tsugu made a lot of mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzu was like this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzu Yuzu Yuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, it happens every year, Miki\Nand Miku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you by your name so it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you called Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm called Miki
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujihira
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one else but Fujihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when everyone makes a\Nmistake
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one I'm particularly curious\Nabout is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujihira
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday at the voice recording session
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujihira's shocking video
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't seen it, you might be\Nable to see it someday
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a video of Fujihira linking with\Nchimpanzees
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing, it was interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can see it someday
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okada was being teased until now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find a new Measubako Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk about Okada this year as\Nwell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aritomo, you have a lot of things you\Nwant to say in this show
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzu, please show us the front of the\Nstage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm scared of moving" or "They're\Naiming at me"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm too scared"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a moving thing on the stage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Are they aiming at me?" or "I'm scared"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all aiming at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't leave them in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really scared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm really scared, so come this way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you might have to\Nmake it pitch black
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not used to it yet, are you\Nsurprised by the lighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really scared
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the countryside, so you know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to Aso
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aso is pretty scary
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'll do it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aso, you're a bit nervous right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only top student here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They give it to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because she eats a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was eating a lot of what Soyou\Ngave me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give it to Maya, she'll\Ndefinitely eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit of a trap, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to give it to her, aren't\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd have to give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But Aso is the one who eats the most,\Nisn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone eats a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone eats a lot, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We add snacks and buy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We buy new things at the convenience\Nstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little funny, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important year for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a funny DVD when you\Ngraduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep accepting more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have one, Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's someone's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "Where did my notebook go?" and\Nhe said, "Oh, Suu ate it."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of strategy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one who's looking for it is\Npretty desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, did you eat it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it irritating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're desperate, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to go down that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you suddenly making a fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that comment about Yoshida's\Nfood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you feel when you said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's popular among me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I ate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, there are people who are\Nreally desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be people who are like,\N"Don't step on my contacts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat it, it might be like, "Don't\Neat it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to play a game? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have eggs, right? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been eating a lot for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, you might have been wearing a\Ncat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of your seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yamaide's fault. Yamaide said it\Nwith a funny smile, so she forgot the\Nmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamaide, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the moment she said it, Tanaka\Nlooked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was able to follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I could hear Tanaka's loud\Nvoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It would have been better if you didn't\Nsay anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it until you're in 9th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't. I'll do it this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with Aso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida and I are really popular right\Nnow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikurare? Chikurareri? That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikurareri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sing a song when I get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, taking a bath makes you feel\Nbetter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want to sing a song to make me\Nfeel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been bothered by it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a schedule, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the standard, but how long\Ndo you usually sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sing for more than 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I sing for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family will be attracted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm often told that I'm noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're long and noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm often told that I'm a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you sing seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of songs do you sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I sing Sakura's songs and songs that I'm\Naddicted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I sing songs with a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little embarrassing, but I don't\Nget stressed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one's bothering you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can just eat your stress and\Ncome to Flesh Monday with a face like\Nthis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the people in the neighborhood\Nsay, "I can hear Maya's voice again."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Asou is bad at it, so it's\Nokay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a time limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't feel like you can't\Nsleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have time, so you can take\Nturns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Yoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida hasn't gone to the second floor\Nyet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll get there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still watching, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked everyone what it was, but it was\Nreturned before the graduation ceremony,\Nso I was a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, wait a minute. I think\Nyou need to explain a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a 2015 Road to T-shirt, but that\NT-shirt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Yoshida's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my Road to T-shirt is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was like, "I don't know!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, "There's no such thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom got mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years ago was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in 2015.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When she passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She passed away before Megu-chan's\Ngraduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So she had it at home for 2 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,XS!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan is tall, so I thought she\Nwouldn't be able to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when Okada realized that it was\NYoshida's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was a time when he couldn't\Nsay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have said "I'm going to\Ngraduate" or "I can forgive anything\Nnow"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have said it at that timing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I read a letter from Okada
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It said "Trick Yoshida"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.56,0:22:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "I don't mind if you trick\NYoshida this year"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep that kind of message
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still people like that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so Okada is the one who's missing\Nout?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, there are a lot of people\Nwho are missing out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're upset because you got scolded?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all Okada's fault, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also my fault for being sick
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the same
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mori-sensei's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aritomo-san, can you stop being so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stop being so dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's continue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no more, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Aritomo, it's fine
