Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.10,0:33:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know what's so attractive\Nabout it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.10,0:33:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.44,0:33:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to do it a lot when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.44,0:33:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.44,0:33:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.44,0:33:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it before, but when I get\Nolder, it's kind of annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.44,0:33:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty, but you can see it on the\Ntrain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.44,0:33:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.44,0:34:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close to the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.44,0:34:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm satisfied with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.36,0:34:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.36,0:34:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.36,0:34:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to buy Jagabutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.36,0:34:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.88,0:34:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.88,0:34:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I've been there, I've been to\Npicnics.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.88,0:34:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.88,0:34:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherry blossoms are really cute, aren't\Nthey?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.88,0:34:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The colors are a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.88,0:34:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really fun to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.88,0:34:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.88,0:34:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I played with Momoe today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.88,0:35:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I played with Momoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.09,0:35:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You were happy, right? You were like, "I\Nlove you, I love you, what's wrong with\Nyou?"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.09,0:35:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.09,0:35:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you discover your charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.09,0:35:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate shaved ice, but it was really\Ncold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.09,0:35:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop sneezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.09,0:35:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And my hiccups were like, "Ugh, ugh."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.09,0:35:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bad memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.09,0:35:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the second dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.74,0:35:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the 20th dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.40,0:36:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first Hacchaki project in\N2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.40,0:36:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a variety of products.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.40,0:36:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.40,0:36:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sell the products to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.40,0:36:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will decide the winner at the point\Nwhere I want to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.40,0:36:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a good vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.40,0:36:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Yoshida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.40,0:36:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.03,0:36:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you seen this in the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.03,0:36:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy it and sell it for real
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.03,0:36:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cut it with a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.03,0:36:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At the supermarket?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.03,0:36:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.03,0:36:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to the supermarket, you can\Nbuy it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.03,0:36:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can grill it and eat it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.03,0:36:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it well
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.03,0:37:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural to be able to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.19,0:37:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aritomo, you're not talking at all
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.19,0:37:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's explain the points
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.19,0:37:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a live broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.19,0:37:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we'll start with a small talk
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.19,0:37:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to not make them nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.19,0:37:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get too close, it'll be hard to\Nrefuse
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.19,0:37:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And the point is to make it easy to hear\Nyour voice
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.19,0:37:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, you've been doing well lately,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.19,0:37:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.70,0:37:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't talking just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.70,0:37:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were kind of blabbering just now
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.70,0:37:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And point 3
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.70,0:37:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out what the customer is looking\Nfor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.70,0:37:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out what the customer is looking\Nfor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.70,0:37:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out what the customer is looking\Nfor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.70,0:37:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.70,0:37:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And point 4
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.70,0:37:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The price is the last one
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.70,0:37:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have a conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.74,0:37:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some people who say the price\Nis too high
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.74,0:38:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are some people who say the\Nprice is too low
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.74,0:38:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to use this as a reference\Npoint and sell it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.74,0:38:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it! You can use any of the\Nproducts here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.74,0:38:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things but it's hard\Nto sell
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.74,0:38:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you can buy this often
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.54,0:38:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.54,0:38:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anitomo, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.54,0:38:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Akindo, show us your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.54,0:38:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what kind of person\Nyou are or what kind of motivation you\Nhave
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.54,0:38:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if it's a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.54,0:38:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just choose a character that's easy to\Nsell
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.54,0:38:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone that I can easily play
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.54,0:38:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.67,0:38:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.67,0:38:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it flat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.67,0:39:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.67,0:39:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is pay day so I have a lot of\Nmoney
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.67,0:39:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.67,0:39:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.67,0:39:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too scary
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.67,0:39:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.67,0:39:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hit you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.28,0:39:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hit you with my grandson's\Nhand
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.28,0:39:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.28,0:39:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is pay day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.28,0:39:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.28,0:39:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.28,0:39:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is pay day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.28,0:39:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be extravagant
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.28,0:39:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.28,0:39:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a novelist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.28,0:39:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you do ego-searching
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do a lot of ego-searching
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.28,0:39:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You do
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.28,0:39:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I get hit a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.67,0:39:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you'll be quite depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.67,0:39:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.67,0:39:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.67,0:39:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She can speak
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.67,0:39:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She can speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.67,0:40:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I talk to her, will she answer when\Nshe's depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.67,0:40:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I try?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.67,0:40:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got scolded by the editor today
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.67,0:40:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Are you okay? Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.67,0:40:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do my best, but how can I\Nwrite a good novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.67,0:40:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.29,0:40:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.29,0:40:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.29,0:40:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you selling right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.29,0:40:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.29,0:40:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.29,0:40:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're selling a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.29,0:40:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.29,0:40:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Kuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.29,0:40:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuma will comfort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.29,0:40:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if you use this, Kuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.29,0:40:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.29,0:40:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This voice is tiring, so can I speak\Nnormally?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.29,0:40:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.29,0:40:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use this perfume...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.26,0:40:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make me angry, and it sells\Nwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.26,0:40:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I look it up on Egosa, I can\Nonly write good things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.26,0:40:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.26,0:41:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you buy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.26,0:41:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.26,0:41:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's attractive. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.26,0:41:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.26,0:41:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is it for a set?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.26,0:41:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you buy it on Amazon...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.26,0:41:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying it in a small voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you buy it on Amazon...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.06,0:41:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 80,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.06,0:41:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk and it's good for your ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.06,0:41:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you buy it here, it's 79,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.06,0:41:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy it for 1,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.06,0:41:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.06,0:41:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.06,0:41:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.06,0:41:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I did my best, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.06,0:41:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.92,0:41:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you don't talk to people who\Ncome.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.92,0:41:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you get irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.92,0:41:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.92,0:42:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a strategy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.92,0:42:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.92,0:42:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter which one sells, you decided\Nto follow the person's mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.92,0:42:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I made time for everyone to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.92,0:42:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You made time for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.92,0:42:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.94,0:42:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job as a top batter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.94,0:42:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of pattern is rude to say in\NUR.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.94,0:42:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say "I'm tired" all of a\Nsudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.94,0:42:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was fun to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.94,0:42:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.94,0:42:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can add the effect on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.94,0:42:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.48,0:42:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that was a good example.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.48,0:43:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,From the perspective of buying it, I\Nwould never buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.48,0:43:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.48,0:43:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me feel like I'm buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.48,0:43:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.48,0:43:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadakai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.48,0:43:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.48,0:43:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.54,0:43:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a difficult one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.54,0:43:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.54,0:43:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to decide, but\Nplease choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.54,0:43:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A kind customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.54,0:43:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.54,0:43:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.54,0:43:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.54,0:43:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is my wife's wedding anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.76,0:43:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I want to buy a lot of\Nthings.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.76,0:43:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.76,0:43:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.76,0:43:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.76,0:43:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.76,0:43:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.76,0:43:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm looking for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.76,0:43:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.76,0:43:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give this bear to your\Nwife?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.76,0:44:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife is the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.76,0:44:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She is 40 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.76,0:44:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look like a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.76,0:44:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.76,0:44:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot these days, so if you wear\Nthis, it'll be cool
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.08,0:44:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this can be used as a fan
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.08,0:44:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.08,0:44:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a fan
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.08,0:44:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little too flashy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.08,0:44:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, today is a wedding anniversary
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.08,0:44:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to have a party with this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The bubble generation is a little young
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.08,0:44:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But this flashy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.01,0:44:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything good about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.01,0:44:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't a normal one better?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.01,0:44:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put this on, you'll feel better
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.01,0:44:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel better? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.01,0:44:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.01,0:44:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.01,0:44:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.01,0:44:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll feel better
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.01,0:45:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll feel better
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.01,0:45:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at it makes me feel better
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.01,0:45:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of the product?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.83,0:45:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's similar to what I used to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.83,0:45:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.83,0:45:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife might want something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.83,0:45:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.83,0:45:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wedding anniversary, so I'll make\Nit cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.83,0:45:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.83,0:45:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, 300 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.13,0:46:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried but it was good at the\Nend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.13,0:46:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.13,0:46:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.13,0:46:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it cheap for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.13,0:46:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.13,0:46:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.13,0:46:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You got many points.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.75,0:46:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to be quiet,\Nbut it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.75,0:46:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.75,0:46:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do Aso.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.75,0:46:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do the one where Okayu takes the\Nlead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.75,0:46:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.63,0:46:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.63,0:46:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to look like I'm tired from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.63,0:46:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to look like I'm not Mori-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.63,0:46:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.63,0:46:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.63,0:46:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be Mori-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.63,0:46:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.63,0:46:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.63,0:47:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.63,0:47:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.63,0:47:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.63,0:47:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.83,0:47:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.83,0:47:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your back hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.83,0:47:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.83,0:47:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.83,0:47:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.83,0:47:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.83,0:47:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.83,0:47:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Age is a part of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.83,0:47:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.83,0:47:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher at a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.83,0:47:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.83,0:47:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't teach my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.92,0:47:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of scary ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.92,0:47:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a recommended item here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.92,0:47:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? For a person like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.92,0:47:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.92,0:47:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.92,0:47:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.92,0:47:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you recommend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.92,0:47:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, isn't this pretty old-\Nfashioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.92,0:47:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned? Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.92,0:47:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to computer games, it's a bit\Nold-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.92,0:47:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you play old-fashioned games, your\Nheart will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.49,0:48:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like calming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.49,0:48:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.49,0:48:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm back in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.49,0:48:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can refresh myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.49,0:48:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.49,0:48:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.49,0:48:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I go home, I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.49,0:48:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.49,0:48:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.49,0:48:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How many do you think there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.49,0:48:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 12 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.49,0:48:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You can play with the members of Sakura\NGakuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.59,0:48:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Sakura Gakuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.59,0:48:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.59,0:48:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.59,0:48:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.59,0:48:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of cute girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.59,0:48:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a lot of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.62,0:48:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 9 of us now, but if you look\Nback at the previous years, there were\N12 of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.62,0:48:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to become Sakura\NGakuin?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.62,0:48:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, I call her Maya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.62,0:49:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and Maya-chan kicks like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.62,0:49:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a ball here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.32,0:49:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a teacher called Morihayashi-\Nsensei, who is a bad teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.32,0:49:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best with the image of\Nkicking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.70,0:49:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With the image of kicking the annoying\Nteacher
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.70,0:49:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can release my stress
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.70,0:49:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, isn't it sad because\Nyou're the same teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.70,0:49:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a setting where the student is\Nforced to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.70,0:49:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, but I can release my\Nstress
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.70,0:49:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, but it's fun to do it alone
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.70,0:49:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.70,0:49:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.70,0:49:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.70,0:49:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart is moving a little
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.70,0:49:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The price is a little
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.86,0:49:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tired, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.86,0:49:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to refresh, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.86,0:49:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.43,0:50:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin was really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.43,0:50:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were Fukei-san, I would want to buy\Nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.43,0:50:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have Mori-sensei-ism somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.43,0:50:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.43,0:50:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's better not to be Mori-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.43,0:50:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.43,0:50:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time, so let's move\Non to the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.43,0:50:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.43,0:50:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.43,0:50:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, Tanaka, Tanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.43,0:50:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.62,0:50:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're here as a parent and\Nchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.62,0:50:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enjoy the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.62,0:50:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.62,0:50:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not that tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.62,0:50:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.62,0:50:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How about elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.62,0:50:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine as elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.62,0:50:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.62,0:50:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.62,0:50:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.62,0:50:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You like high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.62,0:50:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida, are you sure you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.62,0:50:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.62,0:50:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.62,0:50:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The team is really modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.62,0:50:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.26,0:51:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I will buy you anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.26,0:51:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your birthday soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.26,0:51:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.26,0:51:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.26,0:51:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.26,0:51:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.26,0:51:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I'm a really good dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.26,0:51:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.26,0:51:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.26,0:51:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.26,0:51:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.26,0:51:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.26,0:51:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a proud daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.26,0:51:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.26,0:51:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.26,0:51:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a complicated face.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.97,0:51:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.97,0:51:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my birthday, but I want to buy\Nsomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.97,0:51:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.97,0:51:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.97,0:51:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.97,0:51:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.97,0:51:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still early in the afternoon,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.97,0:51:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this kind of childish feeling is\Nfine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.97,0:51:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.97,0:51:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.97,0:51:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.97,0:51:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.97,0:51:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.81,0:51:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a small face massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.81,0:52:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting used to having a small face.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.81,0:52:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter already has a small face.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.81,0:52:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.81,0:52:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.81,0:52:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.81,0:52:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything you're interested\Nin?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.81,0:52:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.81,0:52:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.81,0:52:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.81,0:52:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.81,0:52:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.81,0:52:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.81,0:52:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not early.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.81,0:52:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.50,0:52:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You want it because you're a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.50,0:52:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.50,0:52:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care. If you want it, I'll buy\Nit for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.50,0:52:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This product is 10,000 yen, but today\Nit's half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.50,0:52:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,5,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.50,0:52:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.64,0:52:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me three of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.39,0:53:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a lot of compliments for having a\Ndaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.39,0:53:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I get excited when people say that I\Nhave a daughter and she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.39,0:53:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.39,0:53:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it being sold to Yoshida?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.39,0:53:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.39,0:53:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was kind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.39,0:53:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.39,0:53:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get used to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.39,0:53:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.39,0:53:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.39,0:53:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.78,0:53:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mori-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.56,0:53:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that my daughter would be\Nshocked by this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.56,0:53:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.56,0:53:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.56,0:53:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.56,0:54:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.39,0:54:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.39,0:54:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do something like this. Something\Nlike an etude.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.39,0:54:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.39,0:54:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like everyone can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.39,0:54:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.39,0:54:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.39,0:54:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.39,0:54:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The first announcement of 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.39,0:54:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to decide on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.39,0:54:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The first live of 2018 has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.39,0:54:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.22,0:54:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The first live will be held on May 6th.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.22,0:54:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what will happen yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.22,0:54:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.22,0:54:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you are looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.22,0:55:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.25,0:55:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.25,0:55:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that you are scared of many\Nthings.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.25,0:55:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you done something with the nine of\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.25,0:55:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.25,0:55:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A new song, a new position.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.25,0:55:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's a little difficult to\Ndecide.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.25,0:55:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.25,0:55:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.25,0:55:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else you want to use?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.25,0:55:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.25,0:55:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Rakuin 9th Live Video "The Road"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.25,0:55:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Graduation 2017 "My Road"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.30,0:55:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be released in July 2018!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.67,0:55:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a lot of things like live viewing,\Nbut if you want to see it again at home,\Nit's already
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.26,0:55:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can watch it over and over again, so\Nplease check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.26,0:55:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.26,0:55:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at this kind of high-vibe\Nstuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.26,0:55:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.26,0:56:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.26,0:56:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.26,0:56:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.26,0:56:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we're going to continue to\Ncollect the hagaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.26,0:56:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you send it over here and read it,\Nwe'll give you a sticker, so please send\Nit over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.26,0:56:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some of the members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.26,0:56:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.26,0:56:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the ones that you sent over. You\Ngot the ones that you got for free,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.26,0:56:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.26,0:56:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read the hagaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.26,0:56:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.26,0:56:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.26,0:56:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, everyone got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.26,0:56:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get one. It's already\Nout there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.26,0:56:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to read the hagaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.26,0:56:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we got a feel for 2018.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.26,0:56:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.12,0:56:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a feel for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.12,0:56:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to seeing you again in a\Nyear.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.12,0:56:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.12,0:56:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of the sun!
